# 📡 Wi-Fi Deauthentication Analysis using NodeMCU

## 🚀 Overview

This project demonstrates the generation, transmission, capture, and analysis of IEEE 802.11 Wi-Fi deauthentication frames using NodeMCU ESP8266 and monitor mode.

The goal of this project is to understand wireless network vulnerabilities and analyze how deauthentication attacks work at the protocol level.

> ⚠️ This project is strictly for educational purposes and must be performed only in an authorized environment.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Study IEEE 802.11 management frames
- Generate deauthentication frames using ESP8266
- Capture wireless packets using monitor mode
- Analyze packets using Wireshark
- Understand wireless security vulnerabilities

---

